data.description: If you are looking for a spacious home, you have found it.   With over 2100 square feet under air, this house is suitable for a large family.  Built in 2008, it features a tile roof and a newer AC (2021). The den is big enough to become a fourth bedroom.   The kitchen was recently remodeled with beautiful granite countertops, wood cabinets and top of the line kitchen appliances.  The master bathroom has a jetted tub and a separate shower.   Property sits on over an acre of land with plenty of room for a pool.  In addition, there is a lot of space to park an RV or boat.    Location is excellent; near Wilson Blvd shops and the new Everglades Mart. There are currently less than 31 active listings for under $500K in this area.  This home has lots of potential and it's calling for new owners.
